###################### INSTRUCTIONS TO RUN CODE #########################

1) The code uses libpng library for reading and writing images. 
   Ensure libpng is installed before running the code. If not 
   installed, 
   > For Ubuntu, use 'sudo apt-get install libpng-dev'
   > Otherwise, refer this: http://www.libpng.org/pub/png/libpng.html

 2) Run the following commands,

    >   g++ <cpp_file_path> -lpng -fopenmp
    Ex: g++ histogram_eq.cpp -lpng -fopenmp

    >  ./a.out <input_image_path> <output_image_path> <num_threads>
    Ex: ./a.out sample1.png output1.png 2

    